{"tid":1663462,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰略討論] 人權法通過後做咩好","createTime":"2019-10-19T12:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T13:40:31.000Z","uid":190579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7498547e54e97e7f6d5b4eb4c17c0abf8f858809","tid":1663462,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全面升級<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紅黑都要裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n唔係洩憤咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n1. 輸出革命 <br />\n對外make noise，打<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: green;\">抵抗中共商業滲透</span></ins></span></strong>旗號<br />\n經過NBA blizzard 事件後<br />\n鬼佬會有共鳴<br />\n希望佢哋比壓力佢哋政府，令中資更難進入外國市場<br />\n<br />\n2. 打倒政權的支柱<br />\n自政府宣佈緊急法，已經係向人民宣戰<br />\n我哋打緊仗啦，咪撚諗住個光環啦，攬住個光環入集中營咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人認為抗爭已經進入<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你死我亡</span></strong>階段<br />\n其實黑紅藍都要裝修，係先後次序問題<br />\n黃企就炒哂D藍絲<br />\n要令支持政府既人變成社會<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>食物鏈最底層</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢樣野其實對家做緊(e.g.國泰)，所以我哋都要還手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253fe8f8142d6d8ff6507dfbb9b5e5beaf93202d","tid":1663462,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:05:27.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6199f48946ce3afc5c6eb2b3d0402ef00a9402c1","tid":1663462,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"【輸出革命】一齊下載強國文宣圖！<br />\n1020 尖東<span style=\"color: re